00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:08.290
<i>Ne? Sesli mesaj mı?</i>

00:05:08.890 --> 00:05:10.830
<i>Kimden?</i>

00:05:13.900 --> 00:05:17.390
<i>Merhaba... Şu anda, ben...</i>

00:05:18.100 --> 00:05:20.520
<i>Hemen arkandayım...</i>

00:05:25.020 --> 00:05:27.340
